 />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=56f0d34a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fn&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=3718af1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/n</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期日0730 見)"},{"pid":"6a290773b4af61546397fd4c809689f7d9ce36ea","tid":1747733,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"3f8c3810a1eb2d33412c584af90aacb73b9c79b9","tid":1747733,"uid":302917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"支持原居民清算何妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30d110cd9f63fbb758151ce99e124637728c525","tid":1747733,"uid":94168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"推，支持原居民同何妖割蓆"},{"pid":"c26ff849dcf12b0bbd603dfbe37f3b7ace7b4b04","tid":1747733,"uid":257712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffb13bd921e19bab54eef117a544c0e33ca3b7f","tid":1747733,"u