<br />\n一票不投 陀衰家<br />\n<br />\n有關以上選區所有候選人名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk/?utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=social_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dsocial_share&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=c6196689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk/?utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=social_share</a><br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n轉載請註明出處：專業清算師專頁<br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=20ce8197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi</a><br />\nTG：<a href=\"https://t.me/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevengehi&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=2ed5b1a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revengehi</a><br />\n連登：1823專員<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US.<br />\n寧投熊熊烈火，光盡而滅。<br />\n不伴寂寂朽木，默然同腐。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n#何妖 #祖墳 #攬炒 #原居民被攬炒 #何妖搞人地祖墳 #地政總署 #民政總署 #二五仔 #反骨仔 #鄉議局 #清咗721條街數先啦 #執葉 #前博士 <br />\n<br />\n#專業清算衛我城<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n#專業清算師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>麻煩連登以外幫手文宣，<br />\n以下正皮、加推、幫手做，時間無多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出街全部對家街站，死得啦，麻煩認真幫推呢個整合左既行動PO啦，再唔做的野輸死喇：</ins></st